import React from 'react'; export default function Privacy() { return

Privacy Policy

Your privacy matters to us. We are committed to protecting your data and being transparent about how we use it.

We never sell your information to third parties. Our policies are designed to give you control and peace of mind.

Our Privacy Principles

  • • We use your data only to improve your experience
  • • You can request data deletion at any time
  • • Cookies are used for analytics and login
  • • You can control your privacy settings in your account
